title: Opening Ceremony
performances: Welcome Address by Dr. Smith, National Anthem

title: Piano Solo
performances: Chopin - Nocturne in E-flat Major Op. 9 No. 2, Debussy - Clair de Lune

title: Violin Ensemble
performances: Vivaldi - Spring from The Four Seasons, Mozart - Eine kleine Nachtmusik

title: Vocal Performance
performances: Puccini - O Mio Babbino Caro, Handel - Hallelujah Chorus

title: Contemporary Dance
performances: Original Choreography by Sarah Chen, Music by Philip Glass

title: Jazz Band
performances: Take Five - Dave Brubeck, Fly Me to the Moon - Frank Sinatra

title: Intermission
performances: 15 minute break, Refreshments available in the lobby

title: Chamber Orchestra
performances: Beethoven - Symphony No. 5 (1st Movement), Tchaikovsky - Swan Lake Suite

title: Poetry Reading
performances: Selected works by Maya Angelou and Robert Frost, Student original compositions

title: Grand Finale
performances: Combined performance featuring all artists, Special thanks and closing remarks
